	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm currently in Sol A and have come across the swinging blade. I didn't realise that I could improve my disarm skill using it (my sense trap skill failed to find it), so I guess I will be practising my skill while waiting for help with Lynada The Exiled.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>The traps I was referring to are the ones in Echo Caverns where you can find them using your sense traps skill, and once you have sensed then you can then disarm them using your disarm skill.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
